# Google OAuth Configuration
# Get your Google Client ID from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# Steps to get Google Client ID:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project (or select existing)
# 3. Enable Google+ API
# 4. Create OAuth 2.0 credentials (Web application)
# 5. Add http://localhost:5173 and http://localhost:3000 to authorized JavaScript origins
# 6. Copy the Client ID and paste it below

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
